==English==

===Etymology===
English "[[mulching]]" + "[[mower]]".

===Pronunciation===
*[[Wiktionary:IPA|IPA]]:/mʌltʃɪŋ `məʊə | mʌltʃɪŋ `moʊər/

===Noun===
{{en-noun|sg=[[mulching]] [[mower]]}}

# A [[rotary]] [[mower]] that cuts [[clipping]]s into small pieces and [[redistribute]]s them uniformly back into the [[lawn]].
#: ''If you mow regularly, a '''mulching mower''' will be beneficial to your lawn.''

